FOR SALE / LEASE

You have the choice of two properties depending on your requirements as they are both quite different.

Property Features:

LOT 1 – OFFICE FITOUT IN PLACE, GROUND & LEVEL 1
Size:       369m2
Office:  217m2 air conditioned office
Courtyard: 16m2 screen
Warehouse:  144m2* with 6m roller door
Parking:  5 x allocated car spaces

LOT 2  - CORNER POSITION FRONTING TWO STREET 
Size:       521m2
Warehouse:  521m2* with 2 x 6m roller door located at the side and rear of the property.
Parking:  4 x allocated car spaces

These property are located in a prime position at the Portsmith Trade Centre, fronting two Streets with good easy commercial heavy vehicle drive by access to Portsmith. Located approx. 5 minutes to the Cairns CBD and is the main Industrial area of Cairns. 

Constructed as a full clear span building with concrete raft slab, concrete tilt wall, clear full span concrete tilt beams roof frame, steel purlins, insulation on metal deck roofing, commercial grade shop front and electric roller doors, what more could you want under one roof?

Each Lot has it own allocated front fascia signage panels so there is plenty of room to promote your businesses.

Located in each tenancy is their own kitchenettes, toilet amenities, allocated car parking, and energy efficient complaint recycling water storage.

For further information or arrange an inspection, please contact Karen Stabile from CBRE on 0412 626 397.
